# A tool for video subtitle generation and translation

## Prepare
### 1. download video from youtube
```shell
yt-dlp https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zduSFxRajkE&t=168s&ab_channel=AndrejKarpathy
```

### ï¼’. extract audio from the video file
```shell
ffmpeg -i input.webm -vn -acodec copy output.oga
```
  > here is an extension list for the video format and audio format

  > |video format| audio format |
  > |------------| -----------  |
  > |.webm | .oga |

